{"title":"13. Embarazo y enfermedad cardiovascular-2021","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Cardiología/13. Embarazo y enfermedad cardiovascular-2021.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Embarazo y enfermedad\\Ncardiovascular","guid":"ypRHnvzB0r59o3N5QfBSOw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Cambios cardiovasculares\\Ndurante el embarazo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"alteraciones cardiovasculares asociadas al embarazo","guid":"VQzd-xoT8shyXWkka2Qg6w","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"anemia relativa","guid":"FKYGcttxWwhDx1onVv-_PQ","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"aumento de la volemia y, en menor\\Ngrado, de la masa eritrocitaria","guid":"p9v37r9Hffx7z0iRKvLHUg","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"presión arterial media\\Ndesciende ligeramente","guid":"HQdywaK6iEnadoZUhAO0tw","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"reducción de la resistencia\\Nvascular sistémica","guid":"F_m7AKZqJMMHVHFw1CJU-Q","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"aumento de la frecuencia\\Ncardíaca y el gasto cardíaco","guid":"I0lovi0s2dfyNPVHjQSKSw","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"semana 32, el gasto cardíaco materno alcanza el máximo,\\Naproximadamente un 40% por encima del nivel pregestacional","guid":"WQvoq_aYhOUESA9fJDodKQ","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"Durante el parto, el gasto cardíaco puede aumentar hasta un 80% por encima del nivel\\Npregestacional debido al aumento de la frecuencia cardíaca y la presión arterial.","guid":"9uG7Ds5SxuiGbHGZcgsW9Q","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"0","text":"Evaluación\\Npregestacional","guid":"XSfTDl5iUybOoTvm18cirQ","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"consulta con","guid":"","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"obstetricia para embarazo de alto riesgo y\\Nanestesiología obstétrica","guid":"rOGeXStyiGuhXd911X6Y6g","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"